snippet.title: Chip's Challenge - Unreleased NES Gameplay
snippet.description: The first few levels of the unreleased NES version of Chip's Challenge! This game is obviously unfinished (no, there's no audio!), so don't judge it too hard. More info and download here: http://www.lostlevels.org/wordpress/2015/11/13/chips-challenge-for-the-nes/
